Debbie, it's no secret that I have been  singlehandedly undermining all
efforts to cut the cost of health care in America. At last, for good or ill,
we  closing in on a diagnosis and a program. Sorry to be a little vague, but
I want to wait until my situation is clear before I go into detail. I hope
to be more definitive about my future plans relatively soon. 

 

In the meantime, I do intend to participate in the Wednesday board meeting
by phone. 

 

In answer to your question about the committees, I still am willing and
eager to serve on both. But, of course I understand that a director without
these distractions might be a more sensible choice, I will certainly support
a change if it's better for CAP.

 

If you like we can discuss by phone.

 

Richard

 

 

 

